metadata.name: Lucyna Kushinada
metadata.description:
Lucyna Kushinada who is called lucy from Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, one of the best anime in 2022, I was so amazed by the anti mainstream story, the perfect character portrayal made me fall in love

Created by Elhaq September 29, 2022

The collector will get the original JPG file in 5792x8000 pixel.
